(1, 'Calgary Remand Centre', '12200 85 St NW ### Calgary, AB, T3R 1J3', '403-695-2020', '403-695-2100', '<p>The Calgary Remand Centre &nbsp;was built in 1993 and can hold a maximum of 704 inmates both male and female in remanded custody. &nbsp; With certain exceptions all visits are no contact visits at the Calgary Remand Centre. &nbsp;The complex also has addiction awareness and substance abuse programs as well as visitation from Elizabeth Fry and John Howard Society.</p><p><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Regular Visiting\r\nHours?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Varies, call facility for information</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Yes, incarcerated person must first put you on their\r\nvisiting list.&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>How can I schedule\r\na visit?<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">The incarcerated loved one will schedule the visit and\r\nlet you know when to arrive or you can call ahead.&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>&nbsp;</b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Length of visit:</span>&nbsp; 45\r\nminutes </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Number of visits per week: </span>&nbsp;3 visits/week (2 on weekdays and 1 on weekend)</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Number of visitors per visit:</span> 3 (not including infants)</p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit? &nbsp;</span>Cash\r\nand/or Money order accepted, no limit.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Call ahead for visitation information</span>', 'calgary-remand-centre', '20180730082824-calgaryremand.jpg', 1, '0', '2018-03-20 15:51:41'),
(2, 'Edmonton Remand Centre', '18415 127 St NW###Edmonton, AB, T6V 1B1 ', '780-638-5100', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Edmonton Remand Centre was built in April 2013 and is the largest remand facility in Canada with a maximum holding capacity of 1,952 remanded men and women. &nbsp; There are a multitude of programs available within Edmonton Remand Centre including academic, life skills, parenting skills and addictions counselling. &nbsp;Visiting is accomplished through video conferencing at the Edmonton Remand Visitation Center on 10403-172 Street NW. &nbsp; Before visiting an inmate for the first time you must call 705-695-5454 to register.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><br></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Yes, incarcerated person must first put you on their\r\nvisiting list.&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>How can I schedule\r\na visit?<o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">All visits must be booked in advance, arrive at least 15\r\nminutes early.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>&nbsp;</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp;\r\n25 minutes </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visits per week: &nbsp;2 </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: Upto 2 adults and 1 child\r\nunder 18</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit?Cash\r\ncan be deposited at the Automated Teller in the Visitation area for Canteen,\r\nmust know Offender ID Number</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Visit:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.solgps.alberta.ca/programs_and_services/correctional_services/adult_centre_operations/nerc/Pages/VisitingInmates.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.solgps.alberta.ca/programs_and_services/correctional_services/adult_centre_operations/nerc/Pages/VisitingInmates.aspx</a> for more information.</p>', '<p></p><table width=\"100%\" class=\"tbl2\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th><th></th></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:center\">Monday<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:center\">Tuesday<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:center\">Wednesday<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:center\">Thursday<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt: