(3, 'Fort Saskatchewan Correctional Centre', '7802 101 St.###Fort Saskatchewan, AB, T8L 4E6', '780-992-6834', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">&nbsp;</span>Built in 1988 Fort Saskatchewan Correctional Centre accommodates remanded inmates from the Edmonton Remand Centre. &nbsp;There are a variety of educational programs, vocational work and mental health programs. &nbsp;</p><div><br></div><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Yes, incarcerated person must first put you on their\r\nvisiting list.&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>How can I schedule\r\na visit?<o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">The incarcerated loved one will schedule the visit and\r\nlet you know when to arrive or you can call ahead.&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp; 60\r\nminutes </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visits per week: &nbsp;4 remand, 2 visits for sentenced </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: 2 (not including infants)</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit?Cash\r\nand/or Money order accepted, no limit&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '<div><table width=\"100%\" class=\"tbl2\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tbody><tr><th><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:center\