(12, 'Vancouver Island Regional Correctional Centre (Saanich)', '4216 Wilkinson Rd###Victoria, BC, V8Z5B2', '250-953-4433', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px;\">Vancouver Island Regional Correctional Centre has been in operation for over 100 years it is home to 140 male inmates who are both in remand custody and sentenced Provincially. &nbsp;The building has undergone many renovations and there are programs provided to inmates including; education, life skills and personal development to enable inmates to make positive use of their incarceration.</span><b><br></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><br></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Yes, incarcerated person must first put you on their\r\nvisiting list.&nbsp; It takes 1-3 days to be\r\napproved for a visit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>How can I schedule\r\na visit?<o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Visits must be booked at least 24hrs prior to visitation.&nbsp; Call to book a visit between Monday - Friday\r\n9:30AM-3:00PM.&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>&nbsp;</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp; 60\r\nminutes </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visits per week: &nbsp;2 </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: 2 (not including infants)</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit?Cash can\r\nbe deposited weekdays 8:00AM-3:30PM.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Regular Visiting Hours: </p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"9