(17, 'Surrey Pretrial Services Centre	', '57th Avenue###Surrey, BC', '604-599-4110  ', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px;\">Built in 1991 the Surrey Pretrial Services Centre is a high-security provincial remand centre for men awaiting trial but still in provincial custody. &nbsp;The Surrey Pretrail Centre has undergone a number of renovations and currently accommodates over 365 cells.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><br></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Yes, incarcerated person must first put you on their\r\nvisiting list.&nbsp; It takes 1-3 days to be\r\napproved for a visit.&nbsp; Call between\r\n9:15-11:30AM and 1:45-5:00PM.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>How can I schedule\r\na visit?<o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Visits must be booked at least 24hrs prior to\r\nvisitation.&nbsp; Arrive at least 15 minutes\r\nearly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>&nbsp;</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp;\r\n45-60 minutes (Video visitation only) </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visits per week: &nbsp;1 visit per day </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: 2 adults&nbsp; and 2 infants</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit?$150\r\n(Cash and Money order) </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><u><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></u></b></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Regular Visiting\r\nHours</b>&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border: none;\" border=\"1