(21, 'Women\'s Correctional Institution', '31 Routledge Avenue###Headingley, MB R4H 1C7', '204-948-8813', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Built in 2012, the Women\'s Correctional Centre is a multi-level security provincial and federal correctional facility which houses up to 196 female offenders.<br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Do I need to be on an Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp;</span><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Your friend or loved one will send an application form to you through the mail (or get an application at the reception desk). &nbsp;The application requires one valid piece of Government issued photo identification. &nbsp;It may take up to 3 weeks for your visitor application to be approved.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>How can I schedule\r\na visit?<o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">All visits must be booked prior to visitation (sometimes up to 7 days in advance).&nbsp; Book a time to visit Monday to Thursday 8:00AM - 12:00PM. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>&nbsp;</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp;\r\n60-120 minutes </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visits per week: &nbsp;1 </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: 2 (no more than 2 adults or 1 adult plus children)</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit? Cash\r\nonly&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Regular Visiting\r\nHours?</b>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5