(69, 'Provincial Correctional Centre', '508 Sleepy Hollow Rd.,###Milton Station, PE, C1E 0Z3', '902-368-4590', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Opened in 1979 the Provincial Correctional Centre can accomodate 124 male and female offenders in Medium/Maximum Provincial settings.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">All visitors must show picture identification to be\r\nadmitted to the visiting area. No visitors will be permitted without proper\r\nidentification. Visitors must sign in upon arrival and sign out prior to leaving\r\nthe correctional centre.<b><br></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><br></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp; 20-120\r\nminutes &nbsp;(depending how busy)</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visits per week: &nbsp;2 </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: 2 (not including infants)</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit?Cash\r\ncan be deposited at the Automated Teller in the Visitation area for Canteen,\r\nmust know Offender ID Number.<b><span style=\"color:#C0504D;mso-themecolor:accent2\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Regular Visiting Hours: You must fill out a visitation\r\nform before visiting an inmate.&nbsp; Each\r\nUnit has it\'s own visitation time, call to find out when a visit can be booked.</p>', 'provincial-correctional-centre', '20180804101542-correctionalcentre.jpg', 1, '0', '2018-03-20 15:51:41'),
(70, 'Prince Correctional Centre', '108 Central Street, Summerside, PE,', '902-888-8208', '', '<p>The Prince County Correctional Centre is one of the smallest jails in Canada with 18 beds for adult male prisoners serving Provincial sentences.</p><p><br></p><p>All visitors must show picture identification to be\r\nadmitted to the visiting area. No visitors will be permitted without proper\r\nidentification. Visitors must sign in upon arrival and sign out prior to leaving\r\nthe correctional centre.<br></p><p><br></p><p><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp;<br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp; 30\r\nminutes </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visits per week: &nbsp;2 </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: 2 (not including infants)</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit?Money\r\n(Cash) can be deposited for loved ones via automated teller machines at visit\r\nafter 5pm on weekdays and anytime on the weekend, <b>MUST</b> know Incarcerated persons ID number.</p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<br></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Regular Visiting Hours: contact to jail and request to be\r\nput on the list, immediate family, call 24hrs</p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border: none;\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\">Monday</p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\">Tuesday</p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"