(72, 'Établissement de détention de Rimouski', '200, rue des Négociants###Rimouski, QC, G5M 1B6', '418-727-3547xt.56212', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Établissement de détention de Rimouski is a 121 bed institution built in 1995.<br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yes. The incarcerated person\r\nmust first put you on his visiting list, and it must have been authorized and\r\ntransmitted to the visitor desk, so the visitors can register themselves for a\r\nvisit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Book visits 24 hours in advance\r\nby calling extension&nbsp;56212, every day, between 6:00 and 9:00PM. The\r\nvisitation department will provide you a visitation time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Length of visit:</b> Regular Visits: 30&nbsp;minutes. Protective\r\nCustody: 45&nbsp;minutes.<span style=\"background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week:</b> Varies</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visitors per visit:</b> 3 - Immediate family only (and\r\nwives/girlfriends)<b> <o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Ca