(74, 'Centre de détention de Québec (EDQ or Prison d’Orsainville)', '500, rue de la Faune###Québec, QC, G1G 5E4', '1-866-528-7936', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Centre de détention de Québec also known as Établissement de détention de Québec or &nbsp;Prison d’Orsainville is a 761 bed institution built in 1910 which houses both remanded and sentenced men and women serving Provincial sentences.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">(according to: &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.securitepublique.gouv.qc.ca/fileadmin/Documents/ministere/diffusion/documents_transmis_acces/2016/117980.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.securitepublique.gouv.qc.ca/fileadmin/Documents/ministere/diffusion/documents_transmis_acces/2016/117980.pdf</a>)</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><br></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><br></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yes.&nbsp; Only immediate family can visit (as well as\r\nhusbands/wives and boyfriends/girlfriends) previously authorized by the\r\nfacility director (or its representative).</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Book visits 24hrs in advance\r\ncall the visitation department Monday to Friday, between 1:00-4:00PM and\r\n6:00-8:45PM. For the female facility, call between 7:30 and 9:00PM.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b>Length of visit:</b> 60&nbsp;minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week:</b> 2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visitors per visit:</b> 4.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-CA;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Can\r\nI leave cash or money orders at the visitor desk?</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-CA;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> </span><span lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:FR-CA;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Yes</span>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Regular Visiting Hours:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:66.75pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p align=\"center\" class=\"M