(76, 'Établissement de détention de Sherbrooke', '1055, rue Talbot###Sherbrooke, QC, J1G 2P3', '819-820-3100', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Établissement de détention de Sherbrooke &nbsp;is a 314 bed institution built in 1990 which houses both remanded and sentenced adult males serving Provincial sentences.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Regular Visiting Hours:</b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Varies.&nbsp; It is the responsibility of the incarcerated\r\nperson to tell to his family, by letters, the visiting hours to which he is\r\nentitled, depending on his sector.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yes</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>&nbsp;</b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">It is the responsibility of\r\nthe incarcerated person to book visits.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Visitation Information:</b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Call the visitation department\r\nfor more information.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Regular Visiting Hours:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border: none;\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:65.35pt;border:so