(77, 'Établissement de détention de Montréal (Prison de Bordeaux)', '800, boulevard Gouin Ouest###Montréal, QC,  H3L 1K7', '514-336-7700', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Bordeaux Prison (also known as Établissement de détention de Montréal) is Quebec\'s larges Provincial jail. &nbsp;Built in 1912 the Bordeaux Prison can accommodate upto 1,402 male offenders in remanded custody or sentenced &nbsp;to Provincial time of 2 years and under.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Not for the first visit\r\n(immediate family only); then, the incarcerated person must put you on his\r\nvisiting list.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">You must register yourselves\r\nat the visitor desk. Registration hours are:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sectors&nbsp;A,B and C: </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Monday to Thursday\r\n8:20-10:30AM and 12:30-2:45PM </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Thursday night: 5:30-7:00PM </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Friday:&nbsp; 8:20-10:30 and 12:30-1:30PM </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Saturday, Sunday and on\r\nholidays: between 11:00 and 16:15.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sectors&nbsp;D, E, F and G\r\n(except D2): </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Monday to Thursday:\r\n8:20-10:30AM and 12:30-2:45PM </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Friday: 8:20-10:30AM and\r\n12:30-13:30PM </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Saturday, Sunday and on\r\nholidays: 11:00AM-4:15PM</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sector&nbsp;D2: </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Thursday night: 7:45 and 8:15PM\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Friday:&nbsp; 8:20-10:30AM and 2:15-2:45PM</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Length of visit:</b> 60&nbsp;minutes.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week:</b> 1 (protective custody or segregation), 2\r\n(remand); of these two, only one can be during the weekend.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visitors per visit:</b> 4. Immediate family only (and\r\nwives/girlfriends)</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Can I leave cash or money orders at the visitor desk?</b> Yes. You can\r\nleave a cheque, cash (they do not give change back) or a money order; they do\r\nnot accept personal cheques. </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">On holidays, you can only\r\nleave money orders. You must be on the incarcerated person’s visitors list to\r\nleave money, and it can only be done when the visitor desk is open; Monday to\r\nFriday: between 8:20-11:30AM and 12:30-4:00PM. Thursday night: between 5:30 and\r\n9:00PM. Saturday, Sunday and on holidays: between 10:00-11:30AM and\r\n3:00-5:15PM.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Regular Visiting Hours:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border: none;\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" style=\"width:66.75pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Monday</b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" style=\"width:66.8pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:\r\n  none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\r\n  padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Tuesday</b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" style=\"width:66.8pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:\r\n  none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\r\n  padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Wednesday</b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" style=\"width:66.75pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:\r\n  none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\r\n  padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Thursday</b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" style=\"width:66.8pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:\r\n  none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;\r\n  padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Friday</b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" style=\"width:66.8pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left: