(78, 'Établissement de détention de Rivière-des-Prairies', '11900, rue Armand-Chaput###Rivière-des-Prairies, QC, H1C 1S7', '514-494-3930', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Établissement de détention de Rivière-des-Prairies is a 541 bed institution which houses both remanded and sentenced adult men serving Provincial sentences</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">(according to: &nbsp;http://www.securitepublique.gouv.qc.ca/fileadmin/Documents/ministere/diffusion/documents_transmis_acces/2016/117980.pdf)</p><div><br></div><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yes. The incarcerated person\r\nmust first put you on his visiting list, and it takes 1 to 3&nbsp;days to be\r\napproved for a visit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><br></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">No. You just have to come\r\nduring the visiting hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>&nbsp;</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Length of visit:</b> 60&nbsp;minutes.<span style=\"background:yellow;\r\nmso-highlight:yellow\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week:</b> 3.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visitors per visit:</b> 4. Immediate family only (and\r\nwives/girlfriends)</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Can I leave cash or money orders at the visitor desk?</b> Yes. You can\r\nleave cash (they do not give change back) or a money order at the visitor desk,\r\nin Canadian dollars only Monday to Friday, and on Sundays, between 9:00AM-12:00PM,\r\n1:00-5:00PM and 6:00-8:30PM.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u><span lang=\"FR-CA\">&nbsp;</span></u></b></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Regular Visiting Hours:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border: none;\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:66.75pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Monday</b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:66.8pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Tuesday</b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:66.8pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Wednesday</b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:66.75pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Thursday</b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:66.8pt;