(79, 'Établissement de détention de Hull', '75, rue Saint-François###Gatineau, QC, J9A 1B4', '1-866-466-7603', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Établissement de détention de Hull &nbsp;is a 232 bed institution built in 1936 which houses both remanded and sentenced adult males serving Provincial sentences.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p><div><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Regular Visiting Hours:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Varies.&nbsp; It is the responsibility of the incarcerated\r\nperson to tell to his family the visiting hours to which he is entitled,\r\ndepending on his sector.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yes. Before scheduling the\r\nfirst visit the incarcerated person put you on a visitation list, this may take\r\nseveral days. </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">It is the responsibility of\r\nthe incarcerated person to schedule visits. Also, it is very important to know\r\nthat there is only five incarcerated persons that can schedule a visit on each\r\nvisiting hour; so, it is first-come, first-served basis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Length of visit:</b> 30&nbsp;minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week:</b> 1, maybe more; it depends on the sector.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visitors per visit:</b> 2 adults. Immediate family only (and\r\nwives/girlfriends)</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Can I leave cash or money orders at the visitor desk?</b> Yes. They\r\nonly accept cash.<br clear=\"all\" style=\"mso-special-character:line-break;\r\npage-break-before:always\">\r\n</p></div>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Call ahead, visiting hours vary</span></p>', 'etablissement-de-detention-de-hull', '20181220101812-Hull Detention.jpg', 1, '1', '2018-03-20 15:51:41');
