(80, 'Établissement de détention d’Amos ', '851, 3e Rue Ouest###Amos, QC, J9T 2T4', '1-866-491-4221', '', '<p>Built in 2016 the&nbsp;Établissement de détention d’Amos &nbsp;replaces the existing 121 bed detention facility. &nbsp;The new Établissement de détention d’Amos has 220 beds that accomodate both male and female offenders serving Provincial sentences or awaiting court dates.</p><p><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yes. Immediate family only\r\n(and wives/girlfriends) For special cases, you can speak with the head of unit,\r\nat the extension&nbsp;211.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yes. You can only visit an\r\nincarcerated person when you previously schedule an appointment.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u><br></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Length of visit:</b> 60 minutes.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week:</b> 2.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visitors per visit:</b> 3.</p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Can I leave cash or money orders at the visitor desk?</b> Yes, you can\r\nleave money during visiting hours, and you must be on the incarcerated person’s\r\nvisitors list to do so.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Regular Visiting Hours:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cell