(83, 'Établissement de détention de Percé', '124-B, route 132 Ouest, casier postal 70###Percé, QC, G0C 2L0', '1-877-418-9504', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15.2px;\">Établissement de détention de Percé war reopened in 2010 and expanded to offer an intervention program for sex offenders. &nbsp;The&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15.2px;\">Établissement de détention de Percé can accommodate 46 adult male Provincial inmates.</span><span style=\"text-align: start;\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Visits must be booked at least\r\n2 weeks in advance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Length of visit:</b> 60&nbsp;minutes. Depending on the people who are working\r\nthe day of the visit, it can be extended to 120&nbsp;minutes when the visitors\r\nlive very far from Percé.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week:</b> 2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of v