(85, 'Établissement de détention Leclerc de Laval', '400, montée Saint-François###Laval, QC, H7C 1S7', '450-664-1234', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Établissement de détention Leclerc de Laval&nbsp;is a 687 bed institution built in 2014 which took in woman from the now closed &nbsp;Tanguay detention centre. &nbsp;Établissement de détention Leclerc de Laval now houses both male and female offenders serving federal time or awaiting court dates.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b><br></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Book visits 24 hrs in advance,\r\ncall the visitation department between 8:00AM and 12:00PM.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Length of visit:</b> 60&nbsp;minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week:</b> 2, but may be only 1 depending on\r\nclassification of the incarcerated person.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visitors per visit:</b> 3.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-them