(86, 'Établissement de détention de Sorel', '400 Rue Auber###Sorel-Tracy, QC J3P 0S3', '1-855-816-3942', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">The&nbsp;Établissement de détention de Sorel was recently updated in 2017 and expanded it\'s capacity from 88 adult male offenders to 300, in a maximum security Provincial setting. &nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">No. You just have to come\r\nduring the visiting hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Length of visit:</b> 60&nbsp;minutes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week</b>: If the sector where the incarcerated\r\nperson is as more than one visiting hour a week, you can go to both.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visitors per visit:</b> 2&nbsp;adults.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Can I leave cash or money orders at the visitor desk?</b> Yes. You can\r\nleave money orders every day, between 8:30-11:00AM, 1:00-4:00PM and\r\n6:00-7:00PM.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span lang=\"FR-CA\" style=\"color:#00B050;mso-ansi-language:FR-CA\">&nbsp;</spa