(87, 'Établissement de détention de Saint-Jérôme', '2, boulevard de la Salette, case postale 513###Saint-Jérôme, QC,  J7Y 5G5', '450-569-3269', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Établissement de détention de Saint-Jérôme is a 387 bed institution built in 1977 which houses both remanded and sentenced men and women serving Provincial sentences.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Visits must be booked 24 hrs\r\nin advance.&nbsp; Call the visitation\r\ndepartment to schedule. If you want to schedule a visit on Sunday, you must\r\ncall on Friday afternoon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Length of visit:</b> 60&nbsp;minutes during the week and\r\n30&nbsp;minutes during the weekend.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week:</b> 2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visitors per visit:</b> 3.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Can I leave cash or money orders at the visitor desk?</b> Yes, but not\r\nduring the weekend.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Regular Visiting Hours:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalT