(109, 'William Head Institution', '6000 William Head Road###Victoria, British Columbia, V9C 0B5', '250-391-7000', '', '<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">William Head Institution was first intended and used as a quarantine station from 1881 until 1958. &nbsp;The William Head Institution became a minimum security Federal penitentiary in 1959. &nbsp;Since then William Head Institution has been redesigned &nbsp;as a stand alone minimum security Federal institution housing upto 200 adult male inmates.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Source: &nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><br></span><a href=\"http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-5009-eng.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-5009-eng.shtml</a><span style=\"color: inherit;\"><br></span><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"><br></p>', 'Call ahead for visitor information', 'william-head-institution', '20180812074051-williamheadinstitution2-jpg.jpg', 1, '0', '2018-03-20 15:51:41'),
(110, 'Kwìkwèxwelhp Healing Village', 'PO Box 110 , Harrison Mills###British Columbia, V0M 1L0', '604-796-1650', '', '<div>The institution originally opened as Elbow Lake Institution in 1976. In 2001, Elbow Lake Institution was renamed Kwìkwèxwelhp Healing Village and has the only longhouse within Canada’s correctional facilities. The institution is known as the fifth longhouse on the traditional territory of Sts’ailes.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Kwìkwèxwelhp Healing Village is a standalone minimum security facility that does not conform to any of the traditional complex design features.</div><div><br></div><div>Source: &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-5004-eng.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-5004-eng.shtml</a></div>', 'Call ahead for visitation information', 'kwikwexwelhp-healing-village', '', 1, '0', '2018-03-20 15:51:41'),
(111, 'Fraser Valley Institution for Women ', '33344 King Road###Abbotsford, British Columbia, V2S 6J5', '604-851-6000', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Fraser Valley Institution opened it\'s doors in 2004 as a minimum, medium and maximum Federal penitentiary for exclusively women inmates. &nbsp;Fraser Valley institution can accommodate 112 female offenders.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Source: &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-5001-eng.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-5001-eng.shtml</a></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><br></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting\r\napplication form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then\r\na child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Click here to download any\r\nofficial forms from Correctional Service Canada: </span></b><a href=\"https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml\">https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca