(113, 'Stony Mountain Institution  (Minimum)', 'Highway 7, PO Box 72###Stony Mountain, Manitoba, R0C 3A0', '(204) 344-5111', '', '<p>Stony Mountain Institution commenced operations in 1877. &nbsp;It is a Maximum, Medium and Minimum Federal Penitentiary which can accommodate approximately 797 adult male inmates serving Federal sentences of more than 2 years.</p><p><b><br></b></p><p><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp;</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting\r\napplication form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then\r\na child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Click here to download any\r\nofficial forms from Correctional Service Canada: </span></b><a href=\"https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml\">https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>How can I schedule\r\na visit?<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Yes, visiting application from must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then a child\r\nwaiver&nbsp; application must be filled out\r\nfor the child as well.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp;\r\n20 minutes </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visits per week: &nbsp;2 </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: 2 (not including infants)</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit?$300\r\n(Cash only)&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Visitation hours vary, call ahead</p>', 'stony-mountain-institution', '20180812073858-stony-mountain-institution.jpg', 1, '0', '2018-03-20 15:51:41'),
(114, 'O-chi-chak-ko-sipi First Nation Healing Lodge (operated by the Ochichakkosipi First Nation) ', 'BOX 81###Crane River, Manitoba, R0L 0M0', '204-732-2025', '', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">O-Chi-Chak-Ko-Sipi Healing Lodge helps offenders to heal, grow spiritually, and integrate successfully into the community. There is a strong focus on mental, physical, spiritual, and emotional healing. Importance is placed on traditional Aboriginal values, beliefs, and practices. An Aboriginal architect designed the earthen spiritual centre, which consists of a tipi-inspired central lodge, four residences, and a place for visitors. The design inspires spiritual healing and growth.</span></p><p><br></p><p>Source: &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-4013-eng.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-4013-eng.shtml</a></p>', 'Call ahead for details', 'o-chi-chak-ko-sipi-first-nation-healing-lodge', '', 1, '0', '2018-03-20 15:51:41'),
(115, 'Atlantic Institution ', '13175 Route 8### Renous, New Brunswick, E9E 2E1', '506-623-4000 ', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Atlantic Institution is a maximum security Federal penitentiary which was built in 1987. &nbsp;Atlantic Institution can accommodate 331 adult male offenders.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 14.98px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting application form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then a child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12.84px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12.84px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Click here to download any official forms from Correctional Service Canada:</span> </b><a href=\"https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml\">https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms