(116, 'Dorchester Penitentiary Medium', '4902 Main Street###Dorchester, NB, E4K 2Y9', '506-379-2471ext.2 ', '', '<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Dorchester Penitentiary one of the oldest operating corrections failities in Canada. &nbsp;Opened in 1880 there have been many changes made to Dorchester Penitentiary in recent years. &nbsp;Dorchester Penitentiary is both a Medium and Minimum security penitentiary. &nbsp;The medium security site can accommodate 397 adult male Federal inmates.</span><br></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Source: &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-1002-eng.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-1002-eng.shtml</a></span><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting\r\napplication form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then\r\na child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; ba