(125, 'Beaver Creek Institution - Minimum', 'PO Box 1240###Gravenhurst, ON, P1P1W9', '705-687-6641 ', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Beaver Creek Institution opened in 1961 as a minimum institution but was amalgamated with Fenbrook Medium Security Institution. &nbsp;The Minimum security Beaver Creek facility can house up to 201 adult males serving Federal prison sentences.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">Source: &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-3002-eng.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-3002-eng.shtml</a></span></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp;</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 14.98px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting application form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then a child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12.84px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12.84px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Click here to download any official forms from Correctional Service Canada:</span> </b><a href=\"https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml\">https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>How can I schedule\r\na visit?<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">All visits must be booked at least 48 hours in advance <b><u>by the prisoner</u></b>.&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp;\r\nvaries</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visits per week:&nbsp; Visitors can pick between Monday or Wednesday\r\nvisits and Saturday or Sunday Visits during the week&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Visits must arrive before 10:00AM.&nbsp; They can be admitted again before 12:30PM and\r\nno later than 2:00PM.&nbsp; On Thursdays\r\nvisitors must arrive no later than 7:00PM. Upto 4 adults and unlimited children\r\ncan visit at a time. </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: N/A</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit?Visitors\r\ncan bring cash, money orders or cheques for their loved ones.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:&nbsp; </b>Regular Visiting Hours\r\n- General Population:</p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .