(127, 'Joyceville Institution - Minimum (formerly known as Pittsburgh Institution)', 'Highway 15, No. 3766, PO Box 4510###Kingston, ON, K7L 5E5', '613-536-4046 ', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Joyceville Minimum was built in 1963 and originally names Pittsburgh Institution. &nbsp;The minimum security Federal penitentiary was renamed Joyceville Institution when it amalgamated in 2014.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Source: &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-3007-eng.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-3007-eng.shtml</a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting\r\napplication form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then\r\na child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Click here to down