(129, 'Bath Institution', '5775 Bath Rd, PO Box 1500###Bath, ON, K0H 1G0', '1-866-908-4042', '', '<p>Bath Institution opened in 1972 and shares it\'s property with Millhaven Institution. &nbsp;Bath Institution is a medium security Federal penitentiary capable of accommodating upto 516 adult male inmates.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 14.98px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting application form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then a child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12.84px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12.84px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Click here to download any official forms from Correctional Service Canada:</span> </b><a href=\"https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml\">https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>How can I schedule\r\na visit?<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">All visits must be booked at least 48 hours in\r\nadvance.&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp; Arrive\r\nbefore 10:00AM.&nbsp; They can be admitted\r\nagain before 12:30PM and no later than 2:00PM.&nbsp;\r\nOn Thursdays visitors must arrive no later than 7:00PM.Number of visits\r\nper week: &nbsp;2 </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: 4</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit?Visitors\r\nCANNOT bring cash to a visit only money orders or cheques.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:&nbsp; </b></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:center\">Monday</p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:center\">Tuesday</p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:n