(130, 'Grand Valley Institution for Women ', '1575 Homer Watson Blvd.###Kitchener, ON, N2P 2C5', '519-895-8117', '', '<p>Grand Valley Institution is a Federal penitentiary exclusively for female inmates serving Federal sentences. &nbsp;It opened in 1997 and can hold upto 215 female Federal offenders in a minimum and medium security setting.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:&nbsp; </b>Visitors must call\r\nahead to be given a visitation time slot.&nbsp;\r\nUpto 4 adults and unlimited children can visit at a time.&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting\r\napplication form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then\r\na child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Click here to download any\r\nofficial forms from Correctional Service Canada: </span></b><a href=\"https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml\">https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>How can I schedule\r\na visit?<o:p></o:p></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">All visits must be booked at least 72 hours in\r\nadvance.&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp; Varies\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visits per week: &nbsp;Each visitor can visit the inmate once per\r\nweek </p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: 4 (not including infants)</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money when I visit:</p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-CA;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Cash and Money orders</span><br></p>', 'Please call prior to visiting, as visitation times vary.', 'grand-valley-institution-for-women-', '20181220102350-grand_valley___Super_Portrait.jpg', 1, '3', '2018-03-20 15:51:41'),
(131, 'Donnacona Institution ', '1537, Route 138###Donnacona, QC, G3M 1C9', '418-285-2455', '', '<p>Donnacona was opened in 1986, it is a Maximum security Federal penitentiary that can accommodate upto 451 adult male inmates.</p><p>Source: &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-2003-eng.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-2003-eng.shtml</a></p><p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</span><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 14.98px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting application form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then a child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12.84px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12.84px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Click here to download any official forms from Correctional Service Canada:</span> </b><a href=\"https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml\">https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Visits must be booked at least\r\n24hrs in advance.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><br></p>', '<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Call the visitation department for more information as visitation hours may vary.</span>', 'donnacona-institution', '20181220101213-donnacona.jpg', 1, '3', '2018-03-20 15:51:41'),
(132, 'Port-Cartier Institution ', 'Chemin de l\'Aéroport, case postale 7070###Port-Cartier, QC, G5B 2W2', '418-766-7070', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Port-Cartier Institution was built in 1986 and can accommodate upto 237 maximum security male offenders serving Federal sentences.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting\r\napplication form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then\r\na child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Click here to download any\r\nofficial forms from Correctional Service Canada: </span></b><a href=\"https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml\">https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml</a><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Visits must be booked at least\r\n24hrs in advance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Length of visit:</b> You can stay with your loved one for the entire\r\nperiod of the visiting hour.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week:</b> You can visit your loved one at each\r\nvisiting hour of the week, for a total of 8&nbsp;times a week.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visitors per visit:</b> 3.</p>\r\n\r\n<b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\nline-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-CA;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Can\r\nI leave cash or money orders at the visitor desk?</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-CA;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\"> Yes. cheque or money order only</span>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Regular V