(135, 'Archambault Institution ', '242, montée Gagnon###Sainte-Anne-des-Plaines, QC,  J0N 1H0', '450-478-5960xt.8625', '', '<p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Archambault Institution is both a Medium and Minimum security Federal penitentiary. &nbsp;The Medium security area can house up to 284 adult male inmates.</span><br></p><p><b style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></b></p><p><b style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do I need to be on an Incarcerated person’s visitors list?</b><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 14.98px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting application form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then a child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12.84px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12.84px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Click here to download any official forms from Correctional Service Canada:</span> </b><a href=\"https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml\">https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml</a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>How can I schedule a visit?</b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Visits must be booked at least\r\n24 hours prior to visitation, between 9:00 and 11:00 am.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u>Visitation Information:</u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><b>Length of visit:</b> You can stay with your loved one for the entire\r\nperiod of the visiting hour, but, the visitors that arrived first will be the\r\nfirst to go, approximately 30&nbsp;minutes before the ending of the visiting\r\nhour.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visits per week:</b> An incarcerated person that has a\r\nsentence of 15&nbsp;years and more can have 15&nbsp;visits during a month;\r\notherwise, it is 12&nbsp;visit/month.</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Number of visitors per visit:</b> 3.</p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Can I leave cash or money orders at the visitor desk?</b> Money order\r\nonly.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b>Regular Visiting Hours:</b></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:66.75pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b>Monday</b></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"89\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:66.8pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  so