(140, 'Saskatchewan Penitentiary ', '15th Street West, PO Box 160###Prince Albert, SK, S6V 5R6', '306-765-8000 ', '', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Saskatchewan Penitentiary was built in 1911 as a stand alone Federal Institution. However, since then it has amalgamated and currently has a Maximum security area (which has a capacity of 176 male inmates), a Medium security area (which has a capacity of 176 male inmates) and a Minimum security area (which has a capacity of 324 male inmates).&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\">Source: &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-4012-eng.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/institutions/001002-4012-eng.shtml</a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8px;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Do I need to be on\r\nan Incarcerated persons visitors list?&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Yes, visiting\r\napplication form must be filled out.&nbsp; If there are children visiting then\r\na child waiver application must be filled out for the child as well.</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Click here to download any\r\nofficial forms from Correctional Service Canada: </span></b><a href=\"https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml\">https://www.csc-scc.gc.ca/forms/index-eng.shtml</a><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>How can I schedule\r\na visit?<o:p></o:p></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">First come first serve you do not have to be on a list,\r\nhowever arrive at least 30 minutes early.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b>Visitation\r\nInformation:</b>&nbsp; </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Length of visit:&nbsp;\r\n20 minutes </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visits per week: &nbsp;2 </p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Number of visitors per visit: 2 (not including infants)</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Can I drop off money to my loved one when I visit?$300\r\n(Cash only)&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '<p></p><p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Regular Visiting Hours:</p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n <tbody><tr>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:center\">Monday</p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"91\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:68.4pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-alt:\r\n  solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt\">\r\n  <p align=\"center\" class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align:center\">Tuesday</p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <